author: jeremias
msg: Bugfix: Areas for table-cells that are broken over more than one page are now generated even if all its content is already painted on a previous page. This fixes strange effects like a table grid that is not completely painted.
Some check in the test cases had to be adjusted because the indices weren't correct anymore, since now some previously missing areas are generated.
